{"tid":1006623,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲男人真係好難滿足","createTime":"2019-02-03T06:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T07:38:51.000Z","uid":207313,"like":9,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f52d9d5545b4bc2c418e881a16f0f07e9b385c2d","tid":1006623,"uid":207313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"成日拍拖都係去吃喝玩樂<br />\n一陣豪大大 一陣珍珠奶茶<br />\n過時過節例牌要食餐豪啲嘅放題打邊爐<br />\n你地男仔就話有做開運動 <br />\n好似打波做gym咁 keep到身材姐<br />\n有冇諗過你身邊條女根本冇運動習慣<br />\n而且女仔天生比男仔多脂肪 少肌肉<br />\n仲要成日一同你岀街就食得又肥又油<br />\n係 拍拖就當然係一齊岀去飲飲食食 周圍打卡先開心<br />\n但到你草肥左條女<br />\n就又嫌佢又肥又西成面暗瘡<br />\n着衫唔好睇 嫌三嫌四 比說話你條女聽<br />\n岀街就成日昅啲樣靚身材正嘅靚女<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟你班男人想點呢？<br />\n真係好撚難滿足你嗰喎<br />\n咁唯有祝你搵到個食乜都唔識肥嘅女朋友<br />\n<br />\n奉勸一句<br />\n當你搵到嘅時候可能人地根本唔show你"},{"pid":"fc17f7dd926ec95c6f373f028f652e21cc72e73f","tid":1006623,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T06:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7599d3b95f02ac317baca9677ebbe131cb99c3dd","tid":1006623,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T06:28:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84a09c74a216728a158b93b8fc89feb23703af53","tid":1006623,"uid":154054,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T06:31:07.000Z","msg":"點解唔運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401c3467fff998fd8033757f1340e609e36759cc","tid":1006623,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T06:34:51.000Z","msg":"關我咩事姐"},{"pid":"43828cecbf9a63bd2e85b6830bdf2c6c81e6a9c7","tid":1006623,"uid":176890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T06:38:32.000Z","msg":"毒撚拍拖日日係屋企到時你唔好話悶"},{"pid":"5afc0fe5f45af12451d307c7f3000fb42af553a9","tid":1006623,"uid":13333,"like":11,"dislike"